House of Balloons is the debut mixtape by Canadian singer The Weeknd .
It was released as a free download on March 21 , 2011 , by XO .
The mixtape was also released on his official website .
Its music incorporates electronic and urban genres , including R&B and soul , along with trip hop , indie rock and dream pop tones .
The contributions to the mixtape 's production came from Canadian record producers such as Doc McKinney , Zodiac and Illangelo , among others .
In September 2013 , The Weeknd revealed that the House of Balloons is a real place , located at 65 Spencer Ave in Toronto .